quran[3]{c,v,t}:
  37,0,shuru allah ka naam le kar jo bara meharban nihayat reham wala hai
  37,1,qasam hai saf bandhnay walon ki para jama kar
  37,2,phir dantnay walon ki jhirak kar
  37,3,phir zikar ( yani quran ) parhnay walon ki ( ghhor krkr )
  37,4,ke tumhara mabood aik hai
  37,5,jo asmano aur zameen aur jo cheeze un mein hain sab ka maalik hai aur Sooraj ke tulu honay ke maqamat ka bhi maalik hai
  37,6,be shak hum hi ne aasman duniya ko sitaron ki zeenat se muzayyankiya
  37,7,aur har shetan sarkash se is ki hifazat ki
  37,8,ke oopar ki majlis ki taraf kaan nah lgaskin aur har taraf se ( un par angare ) phainky jatay hain
  37,9,( yani wahan se ) nikaal dainay ko aur un ke liye daimi azaab hai
  37,10,haan jo koi ( firshton ki kisi baat ko ) chori se jhapat lena chahta hai to jalta howa angara un ke peechay lagta hai
  37,11,to un se pucho ke un ka banana mushkil hai ya jitni khalqat hum ne banai hai? inhen hum ne chipaknay gaaray se banaya hai
  37,12,haan tum to taajjub karte ho aur yeh tamaskhur karte hain
  37,13,aur jab un ko nasiyaat di jati hai to nasiyaat qubool nahi karte
  37,14,aur jab koi nishani dekhte hain to thathay karte hain
  37,15,aur kehte hain ke yeh to Sarih jaadoo hai
  37,16,bhala jab hum margaye aur matti aur haddiyan hogaye tokiya phir uthaye jayen ge ?
  37,17,aurkiya hamaray baap dada bhi ( jo ) pehlay ( ho guzray hain )
  37,18,keh do ke haan aur tum zaleel hogay
  37,19,woh to aik zor ki aawaz hogi aur yeh is waqt dekhnay lagen ge
  37,20,"aur kahin ge, haae shamat yahi jaza ka din hai"
  37,21,( kaha jaye ga ke haan ) faislay ka din jis ko tum jhoot samajte they yahi hai
  37,22,jo log zulm karte they un ko aur un ke hum jnson ko aur jin ko woh pooja karte they ( sab ko ) jama karlo
  37,23,( yani jin ko ) khuda ke siwa ( pooja karte they ) phir un ko jahannum ke raste par chala do
  37,24,aur un ko tehraye rakho ke un se ( kuch ) poochna hai
  37,25,tum kokiya howa ke aik dosray ki madad nahi karte ?
  37,26,balkay aaj to woh farmanbardar hain
  37,27,aur aik dosray ki taraf rukh karkay sawal ( o jawab ) karen ge
  37,28,kahin gekiya tum hi hamaray paas dayen ( aur baen ) se atay they
  37,29,woh kahin ge balkay tum hi imaan laane walay nah they
  37,30,aur hamara tum par kuch zor nah tha. balkay tum sarkash log they
  37,31,so hamaray baray mein hamaray perwar-digaar ki baat poori hogayi ab hum mazay chakhain ge
  37,32,hum ne tum ko bhi gumraahkiya ( aur ) hum khud bhi gumraah they
  37,33,pas woh is roz azaab mein aik dosray ke shareek hon ge
  37,34,hum gunahgaaron ke sath aisa hikiya karte hain
  37,35,un ka yeh haal tha ke jab un se kaha jata tha ke khuda ke siwa koi mabood nahi to ghuroor karte they
  37,36,aur kehte they ke bhala hum aik deewany shayar ke kehnay se kahin apne mabodon ko chore dainay walay hain
  37,37,balkay woh haq le kar aeye hain aur ( pehlay ) payghambaroon ko sacha kehte hain
  37,38,be shak tum takleef dainay walay azaab ka maza chakhnay walay ho
  37,39,aur tum ko badla waisa hi miley ga jaisay tum kaam karte they
  37,40,magar jo khuda ke bandgaan khaas hain
  37,41,yahi log hain jin ke liye rozi muqarrar hai
  37,42,( yani ) meway aur un ka aizazkiya jaye ga
  37,43,Nemat ke baghoon mein
  37,44,aik dosray ke samnay takhton par ( baithy hon ge )
  37,45,sharaab lateef ke jaam ka un mein daur chal raha hoga
  37,46,jo rang ki safaid aur peenay walon ke liye ( sara sar ) lazzat hogi
  37,47,nah is se drdِ sir ho aur nah woh is se matawaale hon ge
  37,48,aur un ke paas aurtain hon gi jo nigehain neechi rakhti hon gi aur ankhen barri barri
  37,49,goya woh mehfooz anday hain
  37,50,phir woh aik dosray ki taraf rukh karkay sawal (o jawab ) karen ge
  37,51,aik kehnay wala un mein se kahe ga ke mera aik hum nasheen tha
  37,52,( jo ) kehta tha ke bhala tum bhi aisi baton ke bawar karne walon mein ho
  37,53,bhala jab hum mar gay aur matti aur haddiyan hogaye tokiya hum ko badla miley ga ?
  37,54,( phir ) kahe ga ke bhala tum ( usay ) jhaank kar dekhna chahtay ho ?
  37,55,( itnay mein ) woh ( khud ) jhanke ga to is ko wast dozakh mein dekhe ga
  37,56,kahe ga ke khuda ki qasam too to mujhe halaak hi krchka tha
  37,57,aur agar mere perwar-digaar ki meharbani nah hoti to mein bhi un mein hota jo ( azaab mein ) haazir kiye gay hain
  37,58,kiya ( yeh nahi ke ) hum ( aindah kabhi ) marnay ke nahi
  37,59,haan ( jo ) pehli baar marna ( tha so mrchke ) aur hamein azaab bhi nahi honay ka
  37,60,be shak yeh barri kamyabi hai
  37,61,aisi hi ( nematon ) ke liye amal karne walon ko amal karne chahiye
  37,62,bhala yeh mehmani achi hai ya تھوہر ka darakht ?
  37,63,hum ne is ko zaalmon ke liye azaab bana rakha hai
  37,64,woh aik darakht hai ke jahannum ke asfal mein ugay ga
  37,65,uss ke khoshay aisay hon ge jaisay shaitano ke sir
  37,66,so woh isi mein se khayen ge aur isi se pait bharain ge
  37,67,phir is ( khanay ) ke sath un ko garam pani mila kar diya jaye ga
  37,68,phir un ko dozakh ki taraf lotaya jaye ga
  37,69,unhon ne apne baap dada ko gumraah hi paaya
  37,70,so woh un hi ke peechay doray chalay jatay hain
  37,71,aur un se peshtar bohat se log bhi gumraah hogaye they
  37,72,aur hum ne un mein mutnabba karne walay beje
  37,73,so dekh lau ke jin ko mutnabbakiya gaya tha un ka injaam kaisa howa
  37,74,haan khuda ke bandgaan khaas ( ka injaam bohat acha howa )
  37,75,aur hum ko Nooh ne puraka so ( dekh lau ke ) hum ( dua ko kaisay ) achay qubool karne walay hain
  37,76,aur hum ne un ko aur un ke ghar walon ko barri museebat se nijaat di
  37,77,aur un ki aulaad ko aisakiya ke wohi baqi reh gay
  37,78,aur peechay anay walon mein un ka zikar ( Jameel baqi ) chore diya
  37,79,yani ) tamam Jahan mein ( ke ) Nooh par salam
  37,80,naiko karon ko hum aisa hi badla diya karte hain
  37,81,be shak woh hamaray momin bundon mein se tha
  37,82,phir hum ne dosaron ko duubo diya
  37,83,aur un hi ke pairon mein ibrahim they
  37,84,jab woh apne perwar-digaar ke paas ( aib se ) pak dil le kar aeye
  37,85,jab unhon ne apne baap se aur apni qoum se kaha ke tum kin cheezon ko pujte ho ?
  37,86,kyun jhoot ( bana kar ) khuda ke siwa aur mabodon ke taalib ho ?
  37,87,bhala perwar-digaar aalam ke baray mein tumharakiya khayaal hai ?
  37,88,tab unhon ne sitaron ki taraf aik nazar ki
  37,89,aur kaha mein to bemaar hon
  37,90,tab woh un se peeth phair kar lout gay
  37,91,phir ibrahim un ke mabodon ki taraf mutwajjah hue aur kehnay lagey ke tum khatay kyun nahi ?
  37,92,tumhekiya howa hai tum boltay nahi ?
  37,93,phir un ko dahinay haath se maarna ( aur torna ) shurukiya
  37,94,to woh log un ke paas doray hue aeye
  37,95,unhon ne kaha ke tum aisi cheezon ko kyun pujte ho jin ko khud tarashtain ho ?
  37,96,halaank tum ko aur jo tum banatay ho is ko khuda hi ne pedakiya hai
  37,97,woh kehnay lagey ke is ke liye aik imarat banaao phir is ko aag ke dhair mein daal do
  37,98,gharz unhon ne un ke sath aik chaal chalni chahi aur hum ne un hi ko zair kardiya
  37,99,aur ibrahim bolay ke mein apne perwar-digaar ki taraf jaane wala hon woh mujhe rasta dukhaay ga
  37,100,ae perwar-digaar mujhe ( aulaad ) ataa farma ( jo ) Saadat mandoon mein se ( ho )
  37,101,to hum ne un ko aik naram dil larke ki khushkhabri di
  37,102,jab woh un ke sath dornay ( ki Umar ) ko pouncha to ibrahim ne kaha ke beta mein khawab mein daikhta hon ke ( goya ) tum ko zibah kar raha hon to tum socho ke tumharakiya khayaal hai? unhon ne kaha ke abba jo aap ko hukum howa hai wohi kijiye khuda ne chaha to aap mujhe sabron mein paiyay ga
  37,103,jab dono ne hukum maan liya aur baap ne betay ko maathey ke bil luta diya
  37,104,to hum ne un ko puraka ke ae ibrahim
  37,105,tum ne khawab ko sacha kar dekhaya. hum naiko karon ko aisa hi badla diya karte hain
  37,106,bilashuba yeh Sarih azmaish thi
  37,107,aur hum ne aik barri qurbani ko un ka Fidya diya
  37,108,aur peechay anay walon mein ibrahim ka ( zikar kher baqi ) chore diya
  37,109,ke ibrahim par salam ho
  37,110,naiko karon ko hum aisa hi badla diya karte hain
  37,111,woh hamaray momin bundon mein se they
  37,112,aur hum ne un ko Ishaq ki basharat bhi di ( ke woh ) nabi ( aur ) naiko karon mein se ( hon ge )
  37,113,aur hum ne un par aur Ishaq par barkaten nazil ki theen. aur un dono aulaad ki mein se nekokaar bhi hain aur apne aap par Sarih zulm karne walay ( yani gunehgaar ) bhi hain
  37,114,aur hum ne moose aur Haroon par bhi ahsaan kiye
  37,115,aur un ko aur un ki qoum ko museebat Azima se nijaat bakhsh
  37,116,aur un ki madad ki to woh ghalib hogaye
  37,117,aur un dono ko kitaab wazeh (ul matalib ) inayat ki
  37,118,aur un ko seedha rasta dekhaya
  37,119,aur peechay anay walon mein un ka zikar ( kher baqi ) chore diya
  37,120,ke moose aur Haroon par salam
  37,121,be shak hum naiko karon ko aisa hi badla diya karte hain
  37,122,woh dono hamaray momin bundon mein se they
  37,123,aur Ilyas bhi payghambaroon mein se they
  37,124,jab unhon ne apni qoum se kaha ke tum drtay kyun nahi ?
  37,125,kiya tum b - al ko pkarte ( aur usay pujte ) ho aur sab se behtar peda karne walay ko chore dete ho
  37,126,( yani ) khuda ko jo tumhara aur tumahray aglay baap dada ka perwar-digaar hai
  37,127,to un logon ne un ko jhutla diya. so woh ( dozakh mein ) haazir kiye jayen ge
  37,128,haan khuda ke bandgaan khaas ( mbtlaye azaab nahi ) hon ge
  37,129,aur un ka zikar ( kher ) pichlon mein ( baqi ) chore diya
  37,130,ke aِl yasin par salam
  37,131,hum naik logon ko aisa hi badla dete hain
  37,132,be shak woh hamaray momin bundon mein se they
  37,133,aur Loot bhi payghambaroon mein se they
  37,134,jab hum ne un ko aur un ke ghar walon ko sab ko ( azaab se ) nijaat di
  37,135,magar aik budiya ke peechay reh jaane walon mein thi
  37,136,phir hum ne ouron ko halaak kardiya
  37,137,aur tum din ko bhi un ( ki bustiyon ) ke paas se guzarte rehtay ho
  37,138,aur raat ko bhi. tokiya tum aqal nahi rakhtay
  37,139,aur Younis bhi payghambaroon mein se they
  37,140,jab bhaag kar bhari hui kashti mein puhanche
  37,141,is waqt quraa dala to unhon ne zuk uthai
  37,142,phir machhli ne un ko nigal liya aur woh ( qabil ) malamat ( kaam ) karne walay they
  37,143,phir agar woh ( khuda ki ) paki bayan nah karte
  37,144,to is roz taq ke log dobarah zindah kiye jayen ge isi ke pait mein rehtay
  37,145,phir hum ne un ko jab ke woh bemaar they farakh maidan mein daal diya
  37,146,aur un par kaddu ka darakht aُgaya
  37,147,aur un ko laakh ya is se ziyada ( logon ) ki taraf ( paighambar bana kar ) bheja
  37,148,to woh imaan le aeye so hum ne bhi un ko ( duniya mein ) aik waqt ( muqarrar ) taq faiday dete rahay
  37,149,un se pucho to ke bhala tumahray perwar-digaar ke liye to betiyan aur un ke liye betay
  37,150,ya hum ne firshton ko aurtain banaya aur woh ( is waqt ) mojood they
  37,151,dekho yeh apni jhoot banai hui ( baat ) kehte hain
  37,152,ke khuda ke aulaad hai kuch shak nahi ke yeh jhutay hain
  37,153,kiya is ne biton ki nisbat baityon ko pasandkiya hai ?
  37,154,"tum kaisay log ho, kis terhan ka faisla karte ho"
  37,155,bhala tum ghhor kyun nahi karte
  37,156,ya tumahray paas koi Sarih Daleel hai
  37,157,agar tum sachey ho to apni kitaab paish karo
  37,158,aur unhon ne khuda mein aur junoo mein rishta muqarrarkiya. halaank jaanat jantay hain ke woh ( khuda ke samnay ) haazir kiye jayen ge
  37,159,yeh jo kuch bayan karte hain khuda is se pak hai
  37,160,magar khuda ke bandgaan khalis ( mbtlaye azaab nahi hon ge )
  37,161,so tum aur jin ko tum pujte ho
  37,162,khuda ke khilaaf b_hka nahi satke
  37,163,magar is ko jo jahannum mein jaane wala hai
  37,164,aur ( farishtay kehte hain ke ) hum mein se har aik ka aik maqam muqarrar hai
  37,165,aur hum saf bandhay rehtay hain
  37,166,aur ( khuday-e ) pak ( zaat ) ka zikar karte rehtay hain
  37,167,aur yeh log kaha karte they
  37,168,ke agar hamaray paas uglo ki koi nasiyaat ( ki kitaab ) hoti
  37,169,to hum khuda ke khalis bande hotay
  37,170,lekin ( ab ) is se kufar karte hain so anqareeb un ko ( is ka nateeja ) maloom hojaye ga
  37,171,aur apne pegham pohanchanay walay bundon se hamara wada hochuka hai
  37,172,ke wohi ( muzaffro ) mansoor hain
  37,173,aur hamara lashkar ghalib rahay ga
  37,174,to aik waqt taq un se aaraz kiye raho
  37,175,aur inhen dekhte raho. yeh bhi anqareeb ( kufar ka injaam ) dekh len ge
  37,176,kiya yeh hamaray azaab ke liye jaldi kar rahay hain
  37,177,magar jab woh un ke maidan mein aa utray ga to jin ko dar suna diya gaya tha un ke liye bura din hoga
  37,178,aur aik waqt taq un se munh phairay raho
  37,179,aur dekhte raho yeh bhi anqareeb ( nateeja ) dekh len ge
  37,180,yeh jo kuch bayan karte hain tumhara perwar-digaar jo sahib izzat hai is se ( pak hai )
  37,181,aur payghambaroon par salam
  37,182,aur sab terhan ki tareef khuday-e rab alaalmin ko ( sazawar ) hai
